OL,3,CChief of Police perjury claims to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated by UK force
OL,6,FA complaint alleging that Guernsey's
OL,7,Fmost senior police officer committed
OL,8,Fperjury will be investigated by a UK-
OL,9,Fbased force.
OL,11,FThe claim was made against Chief of
OL,12,FPolice Ruari Hardy in December 2023
OL,13,Fand is believed to relate to sworn
OL,14,Fstatements he made on two separate
OL,15,Foccasions during a 2022 court case.
OL,17,FAlthough it is not yet clear which
OL,18,Fforce will be investigating the
OL,19,Fallegation, under law it must be one
OL,20,Foutside Guernsey.
