OL,3,CChief of Police perjury claims to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated by UK force
OL,6,FIt is likely to take months with Mr
OL,7,FHardy having already announced his
OL,8,Fretirement back in January, expected
OL,9,Fto take place by the end of the year -
OL,10,Fhe will continue in his role in the
OL,11,Fmeantime.
OL,13,FDeputy Prow also revealed that an
OL,14,Fassociated complaint against the Chief
OL,15,Fof Police under the same set of
OL,16,Fcircumstances was already investigated
OL,17,Fby a UK force.
